name: Pulvis Et Umbra Sumus
description:
A photograph of a crow suspended in mid-'kraa' atop a pillar as
two additional crows zoom past

This image was captured during an artist residency organized by 'Emmenge' (fb.me/emmenah) at the developing island resort 'aaaVeee Nature's Paradise' in Dhoores island, Dhaalu Atoll, Maldives, dated 2016.
